com.facebook.buck.test

Class TestRunningOptions.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.test.TestRunningOptions.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    TestRunningOptions

    @NotThreadSafe
public static final class TestRunningOptions.Builder
extends java.lang.Object
    Builds instances of TestRunningOptions. Initialize attributes and then invoke build() method to create immutable instance.

    Builder is not thread safe and generally should not be stored in field or collection, but used immediately to create instances.
